Place your foot on the brake.

widgets.subject: Meeting Room Relocation
widgets.body: Hi Sarah, we have a client coming in from Munich tomorrow instead of next Thursday in the same conference room that have reserved to host an interview.  Since we are planning for an all day workshop, I took the liberty of switching you from the large conference room to the smaller. If this is not okay, can you please let me know as soon as possible?  Thanks! MM
